## Variables de entorno (`.env.example`)
```bash
# Meta – Instagram Messaging (Messenger API for Instagram)
META_VERIFY_TOKEN="<token-para-verificación-webhook>"
META_PAGE_ID="<page_id_vinculada_a_ig_profesional>"
META_PAGE_ACCESS_TOKEN="<page_access_token_con_permisos>"
META_GRAPH_API_BASE="https://graph.facebook.com/v20.0" # ajusta versión

# OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY="<clave>"
OPENAI_MODEL="gpt-4.1-mini"
OPENAI_EMBED_MODEL="text-embedding-3-large"

# DB
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/db"

# Redis (opcional)
REDIS_URL="redis://localhost:6379"

# Vector DB (ejemplo pgvector)
VECTOR_DB_URL="postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/vector_db"
